Safaricom has announced that they are experiencing challenges with M-Pesa services. Customers who access the M-Pesa services on the My Safaricom App, Mshwari and KCB M-Pesa will now have to wait since the services are currently unavailable. "We are working to restore all services as soon as possible. As an alternative to the app, customers an continue to access M-Pesa services through the Sim Toolkit on your phone menu," Safaricom said on Thursday. "We are sorry for any inconvenience and thank you for your patience."